# External sidecar binaries (Tauri `bundle.externalBin`).
#
# Two sidecars live here, one per Rust host triple:
#
#   ffmpeg-<triple>                 — LGPL static FFmpeg (Plan 01-02;
#                                      built by .github/workflows/ffmpeg-build.yml)
#   playwright-sidecar-<triple>     — Node SEA Playwright driver (Plan 01-06;
#                                      built by .github/workflows/playwright-sidecar-build.yml)
#
# Tauri's build script requires BOTH paths to exist per host triple, or
# `cargo check -p storycapture --lib` fails. For local dev, run:
#
#     bash scripts/dev/install-sidecar-placeholders.sh
#
# which drops tiny shell-script stubs matching your host triple. The
# stubs exit 127 if invoked at runtime — they exist purely to satisfy
# the externalBin path check. Release CI downloads the real per-triple
# artifacts from the build workflows before packaging.
#
# All `ffmpeg-*` and `playwright-sidecar-*` files in this directory are
# gitignored (see root .gitignore).
